7-0.query:
SELECT MIN(n.name) AS of_person, MIN(t.title) AS biography_movie
 FROM random_aka_name_1 AS an,
 random_cast_info_1 AS ci,
 random_info_type_1 AS it,
 random_name_1 AS n,
 random_person_info_1 AS pi,
 random_title_1 AS t
 WHERE n.id = an.person_id
 AND n.id = pi.person_id
 AND ci.person_id = n.id
 AND t.id = ci.movie_id
 AND it.id = pi.info_type_id
 AND pi.person_id = an.person_id
 AND pi.person_id = ci.person_id
 AND an.person_id = ci.person_id
 AND an.name LIKE '@param0'
 AND it.info = '@param1'
 AND (n.gender = '@param2' OR (n.gender = '@param3' AND n.name LIKE '@param4'))
 AND pi.note = '@param5';
